Preconditions:
- The input grid is not null.
- The input grid has at least one row and one column.
- The input row and col are valid indices within the grid.
- The input color is a valid color value.

Postconditions:
- The border of the connected component that contains the square grid[row][col] is colored with the specified color.
- The rest of the grid remains unchanged.
- The final grid is returned.